pageContext.claim: “Joe is -- they -- he doesn't even criticize China. I've never heard him even criticize China. He was the one that said, oh, China’s wonderful. China’s this. China’s that. China’s not the enemy. They're not the problem.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump appears to be referring to a Trump campaign video, which we determined was "a stew of manipulated video." Of course Biden had been critical of China.
